Beretta Foundation for Cancer Research and Treatment in return for
permission to use the name Beretta for the line of cars.
   Smith presented Beretta with a Chevrolet Beretta GTU Coupe,
which carries a base price of $15,610.
   In return, Beretta gave Smith, an avid hunter, a rifle and a
shotgun. The statement didn't say how much the weapons were worth.
